<node id="&quot;ELTON&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Elton is a person who experienced hypothermia, returned to camp, and later left for Klaas Billen Bay, conducting experiments on Arctic animals."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a researcher or scientist who recognizes the opportunity to study an entire community of organisms due to the relative scarcity of species in the area."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a researcher studying food chains and ecological cycles, using data from the Hudson Bay Company to understand predator-prey relationships."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a researcher who studied the records of the Hudson Bay Company to determine the ten-year periodicity of lynx and rabbit populations.")&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a researcher who studies lemming migrations and develops theories about their periodicity and population fluctuations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is a scientist who became fascinated by a book written by Robert Collett and began studying lemmings after translating parts of the book."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is an explorer who lands on a smaller island west of the main island called Prince Charles Foreland."&lt;SEP&gt;"Elton is the primary explorer who lands on a smaller island west of the main island called Prince Charles Foreland and spends time surveying with Summerhayes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-0d9fb2d3d3a9552ed8fde9c93b8f8efb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b829398b1a4ba9a515c0a2f3db527528&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-041dbc1d5c450844760cadaea6c2f8fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bedb36fc136bb7c314b807a901c0536&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e43455746665ec422d09c98d6753f95b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7a87b5429f8d0a5624a137e7c209b529&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d578485c62e4dee37f65bfecb459439c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dab6cfe1cab88aebde846ead55782a42</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 8}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 50}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 112}]</data>
</node>
