</node>
<node id="&quot;JACOB&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Jacob is a collaborator with Monod who contributed to the understanding of negative regulation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob is a researcher who makes a significant breakthrough in understanding the mechanism of virus activation and proposes the concept of regulatory proteins."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob is a scientist collaborating with Monod on enzyme regulation and is influenced by suggestions from Leo Szilard."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-4eeff2956121f6bd69a6ab83659363d8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-494c656afa2fa45b32cf5c52326889ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d1852fcdaa63557848de7e718d223a6</data>
