  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Space guides the placement of Beeswax Foundation, which helps bees build combs in the desired pattern."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bee space is recognized in the design of beeswax foundation, ensuring proper spacing for comb construction."</data>
