  <data key="d4">13.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bee Space facilitates the use of Honey Extractors by ensuring proper spacing for efficient honey collection."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bee space is considered in the design of honey extractors to ensure they do not interfere with the natural spacing of the comb."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-118996eccdc1e632c1523338d0325a42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6601c8f8aaba892560d94daa97ed47fd</data>
