  <data key="d4">36.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Jacob and Monod collaborate to propose the fundamental concepts of structural and regulatory proteins in cell regulation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Monod collaborates with Jacob on enzyme regulation, overcoming their initial bias together."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-494c656afa2fa45b32cf5c52326889ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d1852fcdaa63557848de7e718d223a6</data>
