  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Jacob also thinks in terms of Simple Positive Cause and Effect Relationships but collaborates with Monod to overcome this bias."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-0d1852fcdaa63557848de7e718d223a6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
