  <data key="d4">30.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Jacob and his wife visit the Paris Movie Theatre on a Sunday afternoon, providing a break from their research."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob's mind starts drifting from the film to his research in the Paris movie theatre, symbolizing a moment of inspiration."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-494c656afa2fa45b32cf5c52326889ec&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d1852fcdaa63557848de7e718d223a6</data>
